
Use this one for AGX Xavier Jetpack 4.3
https://github.com/furushchev/buildLibrealsense2Xavier/tree/32.3.1

Since cv_bridge can't find openCV.. so an easy work around to install realsense-ros is
sudo apt-get install ros-melodic-realsense2-camera


